                                    <h1 class="section-heading">HCI and User Interface</h1>
                                    <p class="lead section-lead">Personas:
After interviewing friends, and family we managed to dress up 2 personas that would be interested in installing such a system in their house:
35 years old, married for 8 years and has 3 kids. She works part time as a medical assistant. Lives in a house at the outskirts of Boston.Her house has 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a living room and a kitchen.She wants to keep track of presence in her house and hopefully save money in doing so. She is used to electronics and setting up new devices such as the TV, the Rooter… She has heard of the system trough a friend of hers who is really into tech and smart houses.
30 year old, just married. He is a product manager in a tech start up. He just bought a house for him and his wife.The house has a big bedroom and a smaller one, a dining and living room, a bathroom and a kitchen.He wants to have an intelligent house and automise it as much as possible.He has a good understanding in setting up softwares and different systems. He has read on internet about these clever houses and how they can simplify a users life therefore wants to try and see for himself.</p>
